                'kategori'            => 'Sastra',
                'konten_berita'       => '<p class="ql-align-center"><a href="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEimj1xY2ymC5W4SMXv_V7Z8UP0x5METETx7xRokZa9ZOfIbHt7J8_GRGk7pKF-skDaPfAeGn2cV9e7ws17tjA9xIapf2Ave1eC-94S2IT__UYFIIWm2jQihljOEtYsxq0bswMd39eRxCNw/s1600/pamflet1.png" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(18, 149, 201);"><img src="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEimj1xY2ymC5W4SMXv_V7Z8UP0x5METETx7xRokZa9ZOfIbHt7J8_GRGk7pKF-skDaPfAeGn2cV9e7ws17tjA9xIapf2Ave1eC-94S2IT__UYFIIWm2jQihljOEtYsxq0bswMd39eRxCNw/s320/pamflet1.png" height="320" width="230"></a></p><p><br></p><p class="ql-align-center"><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p class="ql-align-justify">Salam Persma!</p><p class="ql-align-justify">Kami pengurus&nbsp;&nbsp;UKM EXPLANT mengumumkan tulisan-tulisan&nbsp;dalam bentuk Opini, Puisi dan Celoteh yang tersaring melalui&nbsp;ajang&nbsp;“EXPLANT KONTRIBUTOR”. Karya-karya tersebut diantaranya :</p><p class="ql-align-justify">1. Puisi:</p><p class="ql-align-justify">·&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Ernawati (Gizi Klinik/2014)</p><p>·&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;RB. Moh. Karimullah&nbsp;(Teknologi Industri Pangan/2014)</p><p>2. Celoteh :</p><p>·&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Windayana H. (Rekam Medik/2014)</p><p><br></p><p><span style="background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253); color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">Selamat kepada mahasiswa yang karyanya&nbsp;terpilih, selanjutnya dapat menghubungi pengurus untuk pengambilan kenang-kenangan.</span></p>',
